overview: ALEC: 5â€™11", 190#, Blond Hair, Green eyes, 25 yo; CHAD: 5'11", 205#, Brn Hair, Brn eyes, 33 yo Cause for celebration! Very popular Alec Powers is back. He's getting older, but he definitely is getting hunkier. What a body! For those who like hairy chests, his is perfection. BG always puts Alec up against very tough, larger competitors. For those who prefer wrestlers with a stocky, rounded muscle look, on the slightly more mature side, Chad Maxwell will definitely do it for you. Chad (AKA Duke Tyler, the notorious TOP in Graphik Arts videos) Maxwell definitely fits Alec's opponents profile. And even though Alec takes two quick falls up front and is definitely a tough competitor, Chad's weight, strength and persistence pays off with a win he barely ekes out by the end of the match. Chad's favorite maneuver: laying his bulk across Powers and pressing him to the mat. For some reason Alec who starts his match with a Big Bang, ends up with a bottom-like whimper.
title: High Stakes Wrestling 14
